data.text:
@bumblebe2362 Hi, you can find the general information regarding what you are required to provide for your flight here: https://t.co/YhT9mVc7De
You also find more detailed information here: https://t.co/I5lXILKAf5
Kind regards, Rebecka

@LudivineMFGE Hello
Contact us on live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or Facebook messenger with your case ID and booking reference and we can help you further.
Kind regards /Anna

@anotherjacko Hello Andrew
We do not know in advance if or when tickets will be released but look out on https://t.co/BlgfvicYhk
Kind regards /Anna

@HelenJUrwin Hi Helen 
Generally tickets are released 330 to 361 days before departure.
Kind regards /Anna

@_venikx Hi Kevin 
Try deleting cookies, history and cache memory. Try with google chrome. If that does not work please contact us on phone or live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards/Anna

@markustests Hi Markus 
If it is an urgent matter please contact us on phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or live chat , if not you can also write to us on messenger.
Kind regards /Anna

@sammaes Hello
Contact us on live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or Facebook messenger with your booking reference and we will check.
Kind regards /Anna

@MagnusBorrby Hej Magnus
Ja det var ett generellt tekniskt fel igår med hemsidan som påverkade flera tjänster.
Med vänliga hälsningar /Anna

@maxwenzin Hello Max
Yes it was a technical error yesterday on web and it can still be problems today regarding some of the services , It is working on a solution.
Kind regards/Anna

@Ondevall Hej Ondevall
Ja under gårdagen var det ett större generellt tekniskt fel som påverkade många tjänster på hemsidan, det kan fortsatt var problem stundvis idag men IT jobbar hela tiden på en lösning.
Hälsningar /Anna

@frihammer Hej Vegard
Klicka på Kundservice/Eurobonus så kommer telefon upp https://t.co/cIkJt9kPnF du kan även kontakta oss via live chat eller Face book messenger.
Hälsningar/Anna

@fish_foe Hi Tobias
Try with another browser or delete cookies and cache and see if it helps. If not please contact us on phone , live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R or Facebook messenger and we can help you cancel.
Kind regards /Anna

@JOtterdijks Hi Jimmy
SAS customer care that handles complaints and compensations have 6 - 8 weeks handling time, we can not affect the time as they handle the cases in the order received. They will reply to you on e-mail.
Kind regards /Anna

@pabloduvias Hello
Yes you can check in for free with SAS at airport.
Kind regards/Anna

@thecadeaus Hello
Contact us on phone , live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or Facebook messenger so we can assist you.
Kind regards /Anna

@eriklidalv Hi Erik
Maybe the issue is solved but if not try delete cookies, history and cache or change browser and see if it helps. Here is phone list if you need to call and book https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards /Anna

@fbpe_mark Hi Mark 
Contact us on live chat , phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or Facebook messenger and we can help you with the correction. If it is booked via travel agency you need to contact them.
Kind regards /Anna

@MrsMartinGore1 Hello, sorry to hear about this long waiting time, must have been some kind of error along the handling.
Please contact us on Customer Service for action: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Best Regards Jan

@bigbananatheory Hello. we realize that flight delays and cancellations can be frustrating and have a big impact on your travel. In attached link you can read about compensation due to a delayed or cancelled flight.
https://t.co/99n9LPxefK
Regards Jan

@jeroenvdmeer Hello, please contact us on Customer Service for help with your account:
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Best Regards Jan

@sam_fowler_97 Hi. Can you try to clear the cache and data for our app on your phone and then re-start the app and login to see if you still get the same type of error(s)?

Best regards,
Anton.

@sam_fowler_97 Hi, if you are experiencing problems with our app please go to the menu and click on App feedback to send an error report to the app developers. You can also try clearing cache and data in the app to see if that helps.

Best regards,
Anton.

@ElenaToponogova Hi. I'm sorry to hear that your baggage is delayed. Please contact our Baggage Service and they might have more information about your baggage, phone numbers are located on https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Best regards,
Anton.

@davidpoblador Hi, if you have a non-refundable voucher that is expired but you were not able to use it you can open a complaint case with our Customer Care department https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh and they can help you investigate what possibilities there are for your voucher.

Best regards,
Anton.

@barnesy5k Hi, please contact us on live-chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your case ID and we can try and help you send a reminder to Customer Care.

Best regards,
Anton.

@LozzMitchell Hi, you can find the latest entry restrictions for your destination at https://t.co/oj06rsDGPg - if you need more information we recommend contacting the local authorities in that country directly.

Best regards,
Anton.

@thecadeaus Hi, I'm sorry to hear that your luggage was damaged. Please go to https://t.co/KQdOdrH9TM for more information about the damaged luggage procedure. If you wish to contact Baggage Service you can find their phone numbers at https://t.co/D7OLjzNpTk

Best regards,
Anton.

@PilMar Hi, at the moment we have longer wait times on the phone lines than usual and we apologize for the inconvenience and frustration that it causes. For general information it is also possible to contact us on live-chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@Bovmeister Hi, we are planning to fly direct between LHR and LLA every Monday and Friday between January 17th - March 14th. These flights can be booked on our website.

Best regards,
Anton.

@SianeeQFSM Hi, we are sorry that you feel this way. If you have any complaints, please send the complaint via: https://t.co/OzrIxYNv63 . 

Kind regards,
Natalie

@trofu Hej! 

Jag beklagar att din resa vart ändrad. I det fallet rekommenderar jag att du ringer vår kundeservice på +47 2189 6400 så kan dom hjälpa dig kolla på ett annat alternativ som kan passa dig bättre. 

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@EloMeliMelo Hi! 

Okay, yes like my colleague wrote too you above, you can use this link too report a delayed baggage: https://t.co/KQdOdrH9TM

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Patric42762067 Hi! 

Okay yes that sounds weird. I recommend that you send in a comment regarding this to our customer care department so they can officially have a closer look at it for you. You can use this link: https://t.co/BTF660MMR4

//Best regards, Dennis.

@elkinthesunset Hej! 

Jag beklagar att du har fått vänta så länge, vi har haft väldigt många som försökt kontakta oss den senaste tiden, så tyvärr har det blivit en ganska lång kötid. Men våra agenter jobbar på det så fort som möjligt.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@bomattsson Hej! 

Okej! Vi ska försöka förbättra det i framtiden. Om du vill lämna dina synpunkter så kan du kontakta vår Customer Care-avdelning.
Du kan kontakta dem här via denna länk:
https://t.co/OzrIxYNv63 välj "General Complaint or compliment".

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@solex_agitator Hi Skaner 
Yes we can book open jaw via phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards/Anna

@Johan72294730 Hej Johan 
Kontakta oss på live chat , telefon https://t.co/z4gOZAAJQJ eller Facebook messenger med ditt EB-nummer så ska vi hjälpa dig.
Ha en fin dag /Anna

@sahal612 Hi Sahal612
Please contact us on phone , live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or Face book messenger and we can assist you.
Kind regards/Anna

@_baelog Hello NB
Contact us on live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or Facebook messenger and we can help you further.
Kind regards /Anna

@Patric42762067 Hi Patric
It is hard to say why it did not work, did you ask the staff? Wifi should be available on board.
Kind regards /Anna

@OscarFoss Hi Oscar
Please contact us on live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or Facebook messenger and we will look at your refund.

Kind regards/Anna

@EloMeliMelo Hello Elodie
Arrival service usually have paper reports if the desk is not open and a box you can put the report in. Please see information via this link https://t.co/KQdOdrH9TM regarding report within 7 days. 
Kind regards /Anna

@Wrightyp5 Hello
You can find our available flights and tickets via https://t.co/saQXo2wpQa and you can mark direct flight when you have inserted date and route, then press search.
Kind regards /Anna

@GuidoDangeri Hello, you can find our phone numbers at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj by clicking on "Customer Service / Eurobonus".

Best regards,
Anton.

@TheSoccerDucks Hi, the Cafe lounge on TRD is unfortunately still closed until further notice.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Anisharingstuff Hi, we are sorry for the flight rescheduling and that we were unable to offer you a new alternative itinerary. If you wish to send us a complaint about this please proceed to https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh to open a claim with our Customer Care department.

Best regards,
Anton.

@SianeeQFSM Hi, please hold and an agent will answer your call as soon as possible. However it might not be possible for them to revert the cancellation so you might have to book new tickets in this case.

Best regards,
Anton.

@LudivineMFGE Hi, customer service does not have insight into complaint cases sadly, please allow some more time for Customer Care to get back to you by email.

Best regards,
Anton.

@CycleHappy2 Hi! A bicycle is considered one piece of checked baggage of the baggage included in your ticket. If the regular checked baggage and the bike exceed the baggage allowance on your ticket - you have to buy an extra baggage for the bicycle https://t.co/N5Z9cNmgWj

Best regards,
Anton

@lucaslugao Hi, I'm very sorry to hear that your flight was changed. Please contact sales and service on the phone for help with looking at new alternatives. Our phone numbers are located on https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@Obach15 Hi, you can check your itinerary at https://t.co/yZoPBVnDMr - if anything changes in your booking you will be notified by email/sms and it will also be updated on that link.

Best regards,
Anton.

@EmmaGwinnell Hi, unfortunately it is not possible to contact us by email, please contact our sales and service on the phone and they can help you with this. Our phone numbers are located at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@JarekMichnowic1 Hi, if you are traveling domestic or within Scandinavia then yes this is possible - outside of Scandinavia there is a limitation of max 1 carry-on item per passenger. You can find more information at https://t.co/gml5ZaEizi under "Changes to our services".

Best regards,
Anton.

@negarabdhagh Hello
Please contact us via phone or by our live chat and we will take a look at what rules that applies for your voucher. You can find our contacts here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind Regards. Anja!

@Emily_Holweck Hi! We can also assist you with this on Live Chat or on Facebook Messenger if you are unable to reach us b phone. https://t.co/z4gOZAAJQJ
Also, I recommend you to edit out your picture to ensure nobody unauthorized can access your booking details.
Kind regards, Rebecka

@terjejan Hej Terje
Kontakta oss på live chat , facebook messenger eller telefon https://t.co/cIkJt9kPnF så skall vi se vad som händer med refusjon.
Vänliga hälsningar /Anna

@bez__za Hello Simon 
You can see our phone number and opening hours via this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj if we are not open you can contact staff at airport.
Kind regards/Anna

@GameGabster Hello
If you mean an e-mail from customer care regarding complaint or compensation you can reply to them. To make a new case you need to use https://t.co/cE0TvFYaMV 
Kind regards/Anna

@michjnich Hi Michael 
Airportinformation is shown via https://t.co/AiYbFomVsK 

Kind regards/Anna

@michjnich Hi Michael
Sorry for the typo. Good you found it. We recommend 2 hours before departure but also check so the airport is open that early in the morning, so you get in.
Kind regards/ Anna

@RichaSparkles Hello Riches
If the ticket is bought via travel agency we can not make any changes because the ticket it not ours. We can only support tickets that are directly bought with SAS. Please contact the travel agency so they can support you.
Kind regards /Anna
